# Frontend (Next.js 14)

## Patterns

- App Router under `frontend/app/`. Shared UI in `frontend/components/`, hooks in `frontend/hooks/`.
- API client: `frontend/lib/api.ts` — use `request()`, `ApiError`, `getToken()` / `getActiveOrgId()`. Sends `Authorization` + `X-Organization-Id` on authed calls.
- Styling: Tailwind only; match existing spacing and component patterns in `components/ui/`.
- Env: `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` is baked in at build time.

## UI copy

Follow README product positioning: *risk co-pilot*, not "dashboard". Keep feature names consistent with the landing page (`page.tsx`).

## Common pitfalls

- Don't read `localStorage` during SSR — guard with `typeof window === "undefined"`.
- Handle `ApiError` status codes: 401 → auth flow, 429 → budget/rate limit messaging.
- Org switch fires `simulyn:org-changed`; subscribe if a page caches org-scoped data.
